      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate interior appointments, reflects a history of meticulous stewardship. This is an investment-grade vehicle for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than excellence.",
