    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You won't find a single scratch on this gem! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
