    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, while the premium leather interior remains supple and still carries that new-car scent. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Mechanically, it is flawless; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records included. Always kept in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. It is not merely 'used'\u2014it is showroom-fresh in every sense, offering a turn-key experience for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
