      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. The F22C1 2.2L DOHC VTEC engine is in peak mechanical health, paired with its legendary close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission. Power is managed via a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis retains its rigid integrity, featuring a double-wishbone suspension setup that provides unmatched feedback and lateral stability. This is a collector-grade example with flawless bodywork and a pristine undercarriage, offering a pure, unadulterated driving experience for the serious enthusiast.",
